    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lentils are cooked, remove them from the heat and stir in 2/3 of the <strong>cultured coconut</strong>,<strong> </strong>2/3 of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and a grind of <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> two-lentil dal</strong></p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
