      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> two-lentil dal</strong> in bowls topped with the <strong>spiced aubergine</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and a dollop of the <strong>remaining cultured coconut</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
